                        <p>I’m a coffee drinking programmer, painter and writer from a beautiful Russian city <a href="http://www.ekburg.ru">Ekaterinburg</a> located on the boarder between Europe and Asia.</p>
                        <p>At the age of twenty I am a student of <a target="_blank" href="http://urfu.ru/ru/">Ural Federal University</a>. My institute is <a target="_blank" href="http://imkn.urfu.ru/">Institute of Math and Computer Science</a>; my speciality is mathematical methods of computer security and now I study a lot of interesting subjects ranging from humanitarian ones like philosophy and history to different branches of mathematics ones and programming.</p>
