                        <p>At the same time I work in a company called <a target="_blank" href="http://www.acs-it.ru/SitePages/Домашняя.aspx">«ACS»</a> as a programmer.  The main focus of company’s activity is development of informational systems for federal customers like The Bank of Russia and The Federal Customs Service.</p>
                        <p>My programming hobbies are web-design and developing applications for iOS platform. You can learn more about my work exploring the sections «<a target="_blank" href="../html/resume.html">Resume</a>» and «<a target="_blank" href="../html/works.html">Works</a>» of this website.</p>
